<p>You will often get <strong>better rates</strong> on <a href="https://www.booking.com">Booking.com</a>, <a href="https://www.expedia.de">Expedia.de</a> or similar sites, especially by booking flight and accommodation together.</p>

<p><strong>ConferenceShare service</strong></p>

<p>Looking to cut costs? Connect with other attendees to split conference costs. Sign up at <a href="https://www.conferenceshare.co">conferenceshare.co</a> to find attendees with whom you can share hotel room, taxi, or car rental.</p>
